{
  "stem": "21349.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My father and I went back home to Bremen, and my brother stayed in the orphan home.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we came back, and everything was mixed up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that's where I found the little passport picture, which I showed you, of my mother, because my mother had made a passport pictures one week before the Kristallnacht, [INAUDIBLE] night.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It seems they should call it [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That's how the Germans called it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because we always wanted to go out and leave.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And everything was [INAUDIBLE] was scratched.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The pictures were down on the floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Everything was upside down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You had to make your way even to get through there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And our bedroom was on the second floor, and we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] This was in November.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The day after Kristallnacht, Goebbels, who was the propaganda minister in Germany, called it off.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But as you know, the Jews had to pay for the damage which they did, and the insurance companies had to give them the money.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So their business was finished.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only I and my father went back home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I started to write letters again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Actually, my brother had bar mitzvah in beginning of October, 1938, a month before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at that time, he had received a letter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At that day, I thought it was a present that we could leave.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the letter said we cannot do very much for you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then when this Kristallnacht came, and even the United States, we called the ambassador for there-- from there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] We started writing again, and we wrote again to all the people whom we had written before, especially to my father's cousin in Canada, that-- what happened.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this time, we got a positive answer.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
